Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
168 Greenhill Road is a substantial 2 storey office building which has recently undergone a full facade replacement creating a striking and modern office building with lift access to all levels. 
The property provides building services and amenities that meet the demands of todays office users.

The available area presents extremely well and has a comprehensive fit-out in place including substantial reception / waiting area, corporate boardroom, several meeting rooms, glass fronted offices, workstations, storage / compactus area and shared IT room with supplementary a/c. Carpeted, air-conditioned and fully data cabled throughout, these professional offices are ready for occupation at a moments notice.

Outstanding natural light, end of trip facilities (including shower facilities, lockers and secure bike storage), signage fronting Greenhill Road, lift access, undercover and open on-site car-parking and an outstanding existing fit-out make this proposition an attractive option.
